    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "March 21, 1960",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Mr. D. Eisenhower, President U.S.A.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Washington, D.C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Dear President Eisenhower:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "As I can't find out any information from anyone, I am",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "writing to you.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "The first part of March I turned over to the F.B.I. a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "colored transparency of the moon and a unidentified",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "flying object for identification. Up to this point I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "have not been able to locate where it is except that it",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "is supposed to be in the proper hands.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Quoting from a letter of March 14 from Major Donald E.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Keyhoe, \"From past experience with photographic evidence,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "we consider it unlikely that you will ever see your pic-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "ture again.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "Also, from other U.F.O. societies I have received the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "same perdictions.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "I would like the assurance that this colored transparency",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "will be returned to me within a short time, as it would",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "be financially profitable in the pursuit of my hobby,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "(cameras and equipment).",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "I am enclosing a clipping from The Detroit Times in re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "gards to this item.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "Respectfully yours,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "[Signature of Joseph F. Perry]",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
